《'''混蛋'''》（{{lang-en|''Bad Ass''}}）是2012年美国[[动作片|动作片]]，导演和编剧都是雷格·莫斯，他同时客串公交车司机，主演丹尼·特乔、查尔斯·达顿、朗·普尔曼。<ref name=JoBlo>{{cite news|last=Walkuski|first=Eric|title=Danny Trejo is a badass in his next movie, titled Bad-Ass!|url=http://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/danny-trejo-is-a-badass-in-his-next-movie-titled-bad-ass|accessdate=December 29, 2011|newspaper=[[JoBlo|JoBlo]]|date=May 5, 2011|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612210711/http://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/danny-trejo-is-a-badass-in-his-next-movie-titled-bad-ass|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Fischer, Russ|title=Danny Trejo is a Fightin’ Meme|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/bad-ass-trailer-danny-trejo-fightin-meme/|publisher=[[混蛋/Film|混蛋//Film]]|date=December 24, 2011|accessdate=December 29, 2011|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117102710/https://www.slashfilm.com/bad-ass-trailer-danny-trejo-fightin-meme/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Staff|title=Danny Trejo Is a Bad Ass as the Beard Man in This Epic Trailer|url=http://geektyrant.com/news/2011/12/24/danny-trejo-is-a-bad-ass-as-the-beard-man-in-this-epic-trail.html|publisher=Geek Tyrant|date=December 24, 2011 |accessdate=December 29, 2011}}</ref>该片的续集《[[混蛋2|混蛋2]]》于2014年上映。

== 剧情 ==
该片讲述美国[[越南战争|越南战争]]退役老兵弗兰克·维嘉晚年好打抱不平、惩恶扬善的人生故事。

